NG0102:2: bo d+hi tsit+ta dz+nya na sam pur+n+na tan+t+ra na ma /

NG0102:30: rdzogs pa'i ye shes thabs chen gyis //

NG0102:49: brjod pa'i brnyan ma nyid dang mtshungs //

NG0102:103: 'dzin med rang bzhin sman chen gyis //

NG0102:131: 'ching bral lta ba gza' gtad med //

NG0102:154: nam mkha' bsam du med pa bzhin //

NG0102:165: 'gyur med rin chen gser bzhin no //

NG0102:176: 'khor ba nyid na ye sangs rgyas //

NG0102:236: 'dod rgyas gsal ba'i ye shes kyang *//

NG0102:238: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen ni //

NG0102:291: rang byung nyid // rig pa mchog gi sbyor ba la //

NG0102:306: gzer chen man ngag theg pa'i skas //

NG0102:308: mngon sum ye shes gsal ba yi //

NG0102:313: sems dpa' rdo rje la bka' stsal pa /

NG0102:318: btsal med rig pa'i rnal 'byor yin //

NG0102:325: sdug bsngal bde ba'i ngang du gnas //

NG0102:327: rang byung bde ba'i sems nyid la //

NG0102:329: bde chen rig pa mtsho ltar zab //

NG0102:333: byang chub kyi sems ye shes rdzogs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0102:334: lta ba bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o // //
NG0102:335: de nas rig pa'i rgyal pos rang bzhag rig pa'i
NG0102:336: don gsungs pa / rig pa'i sems nyid snang med la //
NG0102:338: rtsol med rig pa bsam dang bral //
NG0102:339: ye shes rdzogs pa'i 'khor lo la //
NG0102:340: thig le bde chen bsam mi khyab //
NG0102:341: rol pa bde ldan chu rlabs bzhin //

NG0102:344: ye shes gsal ba'i phyag rgya yis //
NG0102:345: mtshan ma ye shes 'khor lo bskor //
NG0102:346: 'dzin pa'i rang bzhin kun dang bral //
NG0102:347: rang byung snying po g.yo med na //

NG0102:349: ting 'dzin rang bzhag mkha' dang mnyam //
NG0102:350: mi 'gyur ye shes mkha' ltar khyab //
NG0102:351: rtsol bral rig pa'i ye shes la //

NG0102:353: mi rtog rang bzhin rig par gsal //

NG0102:357: brda sgor 'jug pa'i gdams ngag sbyin //
NG0102:359: ye shes 'khor lor mtha' dbus med //

NG0102:363: ngos bzung rtogs dang dmigs 'byed pa //

NG0102:372: lhun grub 'bras bu btsal mi dgos //

NG0102:374: gzung 'dzin gnyen po brten mi dgos //
NG0102:375: thogs med rang byung phyogs dang bral //
NG0102:376: byang chub rang sems kho na @#//

NG0102:380: rang rig bde chen mngon sum gsal //
NG0102:381: 'dod pa'i skabs bral gang mthong tshor //
NG0102:382: rang bzhag ye shes rdzogs pa mthong *//

NG0102:387: dus gsum nyid du 'da' ba med //
NG0102:389: byang chub kyi sems ye shes rdzogs pa'i rgyud las /
